{"tid":1779945,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"一入紅門深似海 - 李碧華","createTime":"2019-12-12T04:22:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-12T04:57:10.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"16e0cd94eb9bfb34efc2ce90ca697f2bf748bc34","tid":1779945,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T04:22:25.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E6%9D%8E%E7%A2%A7%E8%8F%AF/daily/article/20191212/20823384/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E6%259D%258E%25E7%25A2%25A7%25E8%258F%25AF%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20191212%2F20823384%2F&d=WPWOQTheSiAT%2FB2p9vAnANXOzSaib9VKtZEsb4jNOpA%3D&h=034f5465\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E6%259D%258E%25E7%25A2%25A7%25E8%258F%25AF%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20191212%2F20823384%2F&h=acb5aa2a\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E6%9D%8E%E7%A2%A7%E8%8F%AF/daily/article/20191212/20823384/</a><br />\n<br />\n一入紅門深似海 - 李碧華<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20191212/large/1576048550_06a0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20191212%2Flarge%2F1576048550_06a0.jpg&h=128cbddc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n僭建驊在倫敦出席講座PK，企圖藉「甩骹兼骨折之嚴重傷勢」休養三個月至一年，乘機辭職不幹dirty job成殺人犯&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n可惜，她不懂世情更不懂政情惹來恥笑。本來以仲裁建立聲譽，又貪財得財，風流快活也罷，何必在政治權位私利中混日子？<span style=\"color: orange;\">現今被大使館安排（脅持）由倫敦直飛中國首都北京照肺整治，是送中惡法受惠第一人（洗頭機高級過洗頭艇），灰頭土臉回港復工，</span>連累秘婚兩年的79歲老公潘樂陶，公司也涉違反競爭法「巧合」遭查──一切都是自招，正是一入紅門深似海，一人做事一家當，有排受。林鄭陰毒無情，丈夫二子也可當人質以謀大位，但其他人可能沒此修為，唔湯唔水唔甘心。<br />\n<br />\n既曰「深似海」，除非「被自殺」裸屍蒲頭，否則出不來。<br />\n<br />\n世上除了紅門、共門，亦有一入豪門深似海、一入獨門深似海、一入艷照門深似海、一入逃稅門深似海&hellip;&hellip;其實原句是「侯門一入深如海」，出自唐朝詩人崔郊的《贈去婢》，元和年間崔秀才與姑母的婢女互相愛戀，但封建社會婢常被賣予顯貴之家作玩物，深宅大院門禁森嚴，從此難得一見：「公子王孫逐後塵，綠珠垂淚滴羅巾。侯門一入深如海，從此蕭郎是路人。」──現實沒崔秀才獲贈婢女之浪漫，反倒萬劫不復人間蒸發。 <br />\n<br />\n李碧華<br />\n電郵 :mcwriter@appledaily.com"},{"pid":"cecafb3f94b6ee40ec6823cf1f65f9bb0aeddfeb","tid":1779945,"uid":294221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-12T04:57:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/27Y0Qxo.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F27Y0Qxo.jpg&h=f8d2ca9b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">香港人嘅最強後盾</span></span><br />\n<br />\n專攻BNO平權<br />\n幫手解答BNO問題<br />\n<br />\n#MagnitskyAct #BNOisBritish #WeAreBritish #RightTheWrong #SaveBritish #SOSHK<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nJoin us: <a href=\"https://t.me/addoiluk1023\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Faddoiluk1023&d=WPWOQTheSiAT%2FB2p9vAnANXOzSaib9VKtZEsb4jNOpA%3D&h=f00cdf3c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/addoiluk1023</a>"}]}